### Benefits of AI in design:
- Faster prototyping
- Personalized user experiences
- Automatic A/B testing

## 2. Immersive 3D Experiences

With improved browser performance and WebGL technology, we're seeing more websites incorporating 3D elements. This creates more engaging and memorable experiences.

